Name: sequelize
Description: Feature-rich ORM for modern Node.js and TypeScript, it supports PostgreSQL (with JSON and JSONB support), MySQL, MariaDB, SQLite, MS SQL Server, Snowflake, Oracle DB (v6), DB2 and DB2 for IBM i.

Packages.Name: @sequelize/core
Packages.Description: Sequelize is a promise-based Node.js ORM tool for Postgres, MySQL, MariaDB, SQLite, Microsoft SQL Server, Amazon Redshift, Snowflake’s Data Cloud, Db2, and IBM i. It features solid transaction support, relations, eager and lazy loading, read replication and more.

Packages.Name: @sequelize/db2
Packages.Description: DB2 for Linux, Unix and Windows Connector for Sequelize

Packages.Name: @sequelize/db2-ibmi
Packages.Description: DB2 for IBM i Connector for Sequelize

Packages.Name: @sequelize/mssql
Packages.Description: Microsoft SQL Server Connector for Sequelize

Packages.Name: @sequelize/sqlite3
Packages.Description: SQLite Connector for Sequelize, based on the sqlite3 npm package
